cronTime.description:
Cron expression
second         0-59
minute         0-59
hour           0-23
day of month   1-31
month          1-12 (or names, see below)
day of week    0-7 (0 or 7 is Sunday, or use names)
cronTime.title: cronTime

If not set the latest 'draft' version is used

clone.description:
Enable/disable usage of deep data clones
This can be useful to avoid side effects when altering data inside your application
If you are sure that you are not altering the data you can disable this feature to improve performance

baseUrl.description:
The base URL to use for all resources
If not set the baseUrl points to the draft version of the CDN

loaderFileName.description:

headers.description:

skipApply.description: If set to false the fetched config is not applied to the loader but only returned
